my-tasks-description =
    A task overview widget powered by Vikunja for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    Displays upcoming and overdue tasks assigned to the current user across all
    Vikunja projects. Tasks can be checked off directly in the widget without
    opening a browser. Clicking a task opens its detail view in Vikunja via
    the FreeSynergy Browser.

my-tasks-features =
    - Upcoming and overdue tasks at a glance
    - Tasks from all Vikunja projects
    - Check off tasks directly in the widget
    - Due date and priority indicators
    - Click-to-open in FreeSynergy Browser
    - Powered by the Vikunja API
